Node "Node_013"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Message sent by: 00brc@GAInet:HQ. Copy: Why, Robert? You know I'm right, why won't you speak up for me? Are you that worried about your job? Forget the fucking job, Bobby, this is bigger. People are going to die - why won't you speak up?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Back]" linkto "Node_012"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_014"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Message sent by: 69opc@GAInet:HQ. Copy: Hey bobby, are we still on? I had to talk my way out of 'family day' for this, you better not back out on me. I heard about your repremand - way to go! I love the excuse you gave - 'I just wanted to see the sky'. Classic."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Back]" linkto "Node_012"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_015"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Message sent by: 00brc@GAInet:HQ. Copy: I'm going to tell them everything. I know we promised Juliette, but she's gone and this is too big. They won't believe me alone; I need you to corroborate. Help me, Bobby. Lives are at stake."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Back]" linkto "Node_012"  notes ""
              }
}
